high_descs: Turn around, walk to the book shelf, turn right, stop in front of the desk.
Pick up the box of tissues to the left of the lamp.
Turn around and face the shelf to the right of the book shelf.
But the tissue box on the shelf below the compact disk.
Turn right and stop in front of the desk.
Pick up the other box of tissues from the desk.
Turn around and face the shelf to the right of the book shelf.
Put the tissue box on the shelf next to the other box of tissues.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the desk in the corner of the room.
Pick up the tissue box from the left side of the desk.
Go to the next piece of furniture to your left, which is a low cabinet.
Place the tissue box on the left side of the cubbyhole below the top of the cabinet.
Return to the desk on your right.
Pick up the remaining tissue box from the center of the desk.
Carry the tissue box back to the low cabinet on your left.
Place the tissue box on the right side of the opening in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Move two tissue boxes from the desk to a low cabinet.

high_descs: Go to the bookshelf and hang a right to the desk.

Turn around to the cabinet next to the shelf with the disk on it.
Set the tissues on the shelf under the disk on the cabinet.
Turn and go back to the desk.
Pick up the box of tissue on the right of the lamp.
Turn around to the cabinet next to the shelf with the disk on it.
Set the box of tissue down on the shelf next to the other box of tissue
anns.task_desc: Put two boxes of tissue on the shelf.
